History of Art Criticism
E.P. Dutton & Co. | 1964 | English | 420 pages | PDF | 39 MB

This book, the first comprehensive study of the history of art criticism, remains the most important contribution to scholarship in its field. Its author was the first writer to recognize define the distinction between art criticism and art history, new Dutton Paperback edition of Venturi's great work prove invaluable to critics, artists, and students of art and history, as well as to professional art historians
